data.description: Spacious updated 3 Bedroom, 3 Bath home just minutes from downtown Huntsville!  Stainless steel appliances in a spacious open kitchen, luxury vinyl plank floors throughout, isolated oversized master bedroom with 2 walk-in closets! Family room has a fireplace and overlooks the fenced in backyard. Loft area upstairs. Formal living area/ office area.
